{"tid":518441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會籲人大決定「下不為例」 翌日表示用「下不為例」字眼下不為例","createTime":"2018-01-03T10:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T18:32:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3358ff360b36a49446b29e8cd03a770a398bef","tid":518441,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">柒頭</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1373113_1_20180103134307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1373113_1_20180103134307.jpg&h=9e096a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373113-20180103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373113-20180103.htm&d=ryJDW5LW9OMZ1e8iLawrI%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1a34fab5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373113-20180103.htm&h=e66e3fcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373113-20180103.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大律師公會主席林定國昨日接受部分傳媒訪問時提到，「如果人大常委會或特區政府承諾下不為例，可以減低一地兩檢議題帶來的爭議」。林定國接受本台專訪，提到自己有反思言論會否引起對他本人或公會立場的誤會，他承認，「下不為例」並非最好及準確的表達方式，強調絕對無意為公會早前發的聲明做任何調整，降溫亦不是準確的講法。他說不會再用「下不為例」這個字眼，但不會收回言論。<br />\n<br />\n林定國解釋，自己只是想表達當人大常委會的決定不能被改變，亦不會有進一步解釋，如果當局表明這是獨一無二的情況，他認為可以減低公眾對法治信心的傷害。林定國希望外界不要集中在一兩個用字而接收錯誤訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">笑撚死人！精英食屎啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2ee4f802871229f4ddbf9d09b7402d25446a57","tid":518441,"uid":47558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都跪低，你點對得住自己專業<br />\n仲有乜撚野下不為例，影響咁深遠既事都可以下不為例？"},{"pid":"1660dc28306f9943c598c8100109460f0a964c18","tid":518441,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2a2ee4f802871229f4ddbf9d09b7402d25446a57","tid":518441,"uid":47558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都跪低，你點對得住自己專業<br />\n仲有乜撚野下不為例，影響咁深遠既事都可以下不為例？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"最好笑既係, <br />\n<br />\n叫人「下不為例」 <br />\n<br />\n自己首先跪低表明自己「下不為例」 <br />\n<br />\n未見過咁垃圾既, 希望外媒報導下, <br />\n<br />\n等鬼佬睇下呢班自視為「精英」既垃圾, 係多好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e6bdd1d7350c115cb1224f632af3c438abc280","tid":518441,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"其實香港班大律師, 係咪真係以為自己好醒?<br />\n<br />\n行出去外面個世界睇下啦, 佢地自己只係一堆柒頭黎"},{"pid":"b40cebe3878e1b44b6ca1fe2012cec5536c80834","tid":518441,"uid":20867,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"睇見香港大律師食相(食錢銀 食議席 食幼幼 食四方)<br />\n更覺中國維權律師勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0f986c2a67aa57daf1b8c1bb17b956b6a6f753","tid":518441,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"「下不為例」呢4隻字, 本身已經係10級柒<br />\n<br />\n乜野叫「下不為例」呢？ <br />\n<br />\n即係潛台詞係：今次算啦！唔追究, 唔講, 唔提啦！下次唔好啦！<br />\n<br />\n吓？今次算？ 咁仲捍乜撚衛法治呀？<br />\n<br />\n撕毀《基本法》可以「算啦」, 咁呀？<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母, 呢堆乜柒大律師係咪廢架<br />\n<br />\n乜柒公會, 真係食屎啦去<br />\n<br />\n成堆都係垃圾廢物黎"},{"pid":"2f5c7b3203bf4ff055